  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Jungfrau Lodge is on Bed &amp; Breakfast. Each day a continental breakfast buffet is served, and additional items can be ordered at additional charge. A packed breakfast is provided for early departures. </p>
<p>There's plenty of restaurants to chose from in Grindelwald, whether you fancy fondue, pizza or fine dining, you'll be sure to find something to satisfy your tastes. </p>
<p>A welcome drink voucher is provided to use at the hotel bar - open from 5pm.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
