  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Double/Twin Bedrooms</strong> can sleep up to three people, with twin beds and an additional single bed. Choose from north facing, south facing or south facing with balcony rooms. All double and twin bedrooms are located in the main Jungfrau building.</p>
<p><strong>Crystal Building Twin or Austrian Twin Rooms</strong> also sleep up to three people, with twin (or Austrian twin) beds and an additional single bed. These rooms are south facing with balconies overlooking the Eiger and surrounded mountains. These rooms are located in the Crystal Building, opposite the main hotel. </p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are available, these rooms have a single bed and shower stall, and are located in the main building.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Views across the Eiger (South facing) or resort and surrounding mountains (North facing)</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Aircon</li>
<li>All rooms can accommodate a cot (apart from single occupancy rooms)</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
